reviewText: I have all of the Billy Molls DVD's and they are all outstanding! And this is one not to miss, the best ever! This is my dream hunt. Hope to get there one day! Keep 'em comin, Billy!

I hope they send me a refund because I got the right packaging but with a Nick Jr.'s Backyardigan's movie on the DVD. I returned it a couple of weeks ago, still have not heard a word about anything yet... Don't get Duped!!!!
